text: Petracola labioocularis is a species of lizard in the family Gymnophthalmidae. It is endemic to Peru. ==References== Category:Petracola Category:Reptiles of Peru Category:Endemic fauna of Peru Category:Reptiles described in 2004 Category:Taxa named by Gunther Köhler Category:Taxa named by Edgar Lehr
